node.text: Join DeVonn Francis and Joel Moore as they show you how to throw a fun Pride party this year through cooking, music, and decor, while chatting about fun places to go to in the NYC area. This event, along with the sales of the #LimitedEdition Pride watch will benefit the @trevorproject #PrideOnFossil

node.text: Join Lezley Crawford as she takes us through what she’s most excited about for our falls bags!

node.title: Behind the design with Lezley Crawford

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 20, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and purse.

node.text: Our classic, everyday Jolie bag is giving us all the sunset vibes thanks to this new fabric inspired by traditional kilim weave patterns and western motifs.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 19, 2021. May be an image of jewelry.

node.text: Heirloom status, achieved.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 18, 2021. May be an image of jewelry and wrist watch.

node.text: Say hello to Val, the new Vintage Heritage collection. With rope-inspired details and hints of mother-of-pearl, these vintage-inspired pieces will never get old.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 17, 2021. May be an image of purse and saddle-stitched leather.

node.text: Our current fall fave? The Carmen Tote, now handwoven with western-inspired patterns.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 16, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and wrist watch.

node.text: Beat the Monday Blues with some good tunes. You can control your music with the Hybrid HR smartwatch. #FossilSmartwatch

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 15, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text: The new 44mm Bronson offers enhanced wearability without sacrificing any of the rugged details.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 13, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch and saddle-stitched leather.

node.text: Our kind of lineup on a Friday afternoon.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fossil on August 12, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text: Gabby: Wears like a neutral with a little extra flash, courtesy of its new lilac dial.
